# =============================================================================
# .gitignore — Constraint Dependency Graph repository
# Intent: ship code, tests, experiment runners, canonical result JSONs.
#         Exclude AI plans, paper sources, large binaries, build byproducts.
# =============================================================================

# --- AI plans, specs, agent state ------------------------------------------
docs/superpowers/

# --- REMINDER: do NOT commit AI assistant artefacts -----------------------
# The following are intentionally NOT in this .gitignore because the user
# wants control over them per-commit. Check `git status` before pushing and
# make sure none of these slipped in:
#   .claude/                      Claude Code session state, settings, snapshots
#   .cursor/, .continue/          other AI IDE state directories
#   CLAUDE.md, AGENTS.md, GEMINI.md   AI agent instruction files
#   .github/copilot-instructions.md   Copilot instructions
# Also strip "Co-Authored-By: Claude ..." trailers from commit messages
# before pushing if you don't want them in public history.

# --- Documentation / paper artefacts (not code) ----------------------------
docs/
paper/
ns_cdg_draft/
*.docx
*.pdf

# --- LaTeX / build byproducts ----------------------------------------------
*.aux
*.bbl
*.blg
*.log
*.out
*.synctex.gz
texput.log
build.log
missfont.log

# --- Python caches, virtualenvs, eggs --------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.venv/
venv/
env/
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# --- Large data not needed for reproduction (re-buildable) -----------------
firmware/binaries/
firmware_builds/
data/

# --- Trained-model artefacts (large; regenerate with scripts/train_*.py) ---
models/embedder/
models/embedder.faiss
models/embedder.meta.jsonl
models/predictor.pt

# --- Compiled C benchmarks (rebuilt by Dockerfile) -------------------------
cdg_bench_v10
cdg_bench_v11
cdg_bench_v12
cdg_bench_v13
*.o

# --- Local LaTeX/results scratch -------------------------------------------
out/
results/
paper.zip
algorithms.zip
*.zip

# --- Verification-run snapshots (not canonical) ----------------------------
verification_run/
experiments/verification_run/
experiments/baseline/

# --- AI-authored reports ---------------------------------------------------
experiments/verification.md

# --- Anomalous artefacts from prior shell sessions -------------------------
{src,versions,tests,cdg_lib}

# --- IDE / OS --------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~

# --- Local environment files -----------------------------------------------
.env
.env.local
